Return JSON with this shape: {"items":[{"companyName":"...","nseSymbol":"...","newsDescription":"one sentence under 35 words","impact":"Positive|Negative|Neutral|Mixed","impactReason":"one sentence under 35 words","confidence":"High|Medium|Low","sourceUrl":"..."}]}

